      "message": "nit: explitly checking the last try number seems a bit fragile.\nHow about:\n```\nmaxTries\u003d5\nfor i in $(seq maxTries); do\n   ....\n   if [ $i -eq $maxTries ]; then\n```\n\nThat is, assuming the `seq` command is available in the container I guess.",
